# kris.gg is a static Next.js site — it reads no secrets at runtime.
# The only environment input is the canonical origin, used for canonical URLs,
# Open Graph tags, the sitemap and robots (see src/lib/site.ts).
#
# On Vercel this is set per environment in the dashboard (not committed):
#   Production            NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://kris.gg
#   Preview (dev branch)  NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://dev.kris.gg
#
# Locally you can leave it unset — siteUrl() falls back to http://localhost:3001.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=
